data.description: Luxurious 2 family, brick center hall colonial is finely situated on a serine 10,000 sq ft lot with a pavered circular driveway that can fit 6 cars, last home on a dead-end block in the neighborhood of Woodrow. Professionally designed by a world class interior decorator. Upon migrating through the colossal entranceway, you are transported into a grand foyer with exquisite craftsmanship. Custom one-of-a-kind moldings surround every door, ceiling, and window throughout. Attention to detail was a must for the homeowners when renovating! The heart of this home features a custom kitchen equipped with immaculate cabinetry, quartz countertops, Viking and Subzero appliances, a coffee bar and a walk-in pantry. The kitchen seamlessly opens to other spacious quarters including a formal dining room, a formal sitting room, and a family room adorned with a distinguished gas fireplace.  French doors effortlessly lead to a bonus room perfect for all year entertaining while overlooking and leading to the finely constructed back yard with no maintenance Trek decking and an exquisite entertaining area with a gazebo & Jacuzzi. Privacy galore.Located on the second floor, the Master suite is characterized by an opulent sitting area and a glamorous walk-in closet. Furnished with double vanity and a unique walk-in shower with a soaking tub, the on-suite bath undeniably mimics a spa-like experience. Three additional well-appointed bedrooms can too be found on this floor. The property also includes a fully furnished basement with a private home office. Apart from the primary living space, a highly coveted apartment is located on the perimeter of the home's first floor entrance. This 1 bedroom 3 room space includes a private driveway for the tenant.Other amenities of this property include a 3 Zone air conditioning system and a 12 Zone Heating system, FBI Grade Security System.  Tactfully located in close proximity to the Westshore Expressway, to provided with convenient access to NJ
